\"],[\"catatan\"],null,null,1778135171300,\"R/LI-2026050700069/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700069-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700070\",\"LI\",\"ada dugaan pungli sama anggota di konser jawa barat\",\"Jasmien\",\"LSM Perempuan\",\"partnership\",\"interview\",\"bandung 07 mei 2026\",\"sandi pungli\",[\"ditemukan pungutan sebesar Rp 5000\",\"terjadi di gang konser\",\"jumlah yang diminta sekitar 1000 orang\",\"total yang didapatkan dari pungutan liar sebesar 5.000.000\"],[\"lanjut penanganan dan pemeriksaan\"],null,null,1778135218082,\"R/LI-2026050700070/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700070-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",\"BIRO WABPROF\",\"MABES\",\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700071\",\"LI\",\"Tentang penggunaan narkoba jenis ganja \",\"Jasmien k\",\"kanit divpropam\",\"staff divpropam\",\"informasi\",\"jakarta, 2 mei 2026\",\"1234\",[\"menggunakan narkoba jenis ganja \",\"penggunaan di klub malam\"],[\"lanjut ke penanganan\"],null,null,1778137071807,\"R/LI-2026050700071/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700071-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700072\",\"LI\",\"jasmien lagii kena pungli\",\"priyo\",\"ormas\",\"partner\",\"wawancara\",\"banjarmasin\",\"sandi pungli\",[\"jasmien dapat uang hasil pungli sebesar 6.000.000\"],[\"langsung pemeriksaan\"],null,null,1778137526665,\"R/LI-2026050700072/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700072-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700073\",\"LI\",\"Tentang penggunaan narkoba\",\"Jasmien K\",\"kanit \",\"staff\",\"informasi dari staff\",\"jakarta 2 mei 2026\",\"1234\",[\"iptu priyo menggunakan narkoba jenis ganja\",\"ganja digunakan di klub malam di senopati\"],[\"lanjut ke penanganan\"],null,null,1778137722973,\"R/LI-2026050700073/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700073-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700074\",\"LI\",\"Saya melihat anggota menggunakan bahasa yang tidak sopan saat bertugas. Anggota tersebut berbicara dengan nada merendahkan. Masyarakat terlihat tidak nyaman. Hal ini mencerminkan pelanggaran kode etik\",\"test_Andi\",\"Ormas\",\"Hubungan teman\",\"perbincangan telepon\",\"Semarang dari tanggal 16 - 20 April 2026\",\"kode eitk\",[\"Saya melihat anggota menggunakan bahasa yang tidak sopan saat bertugas. Anggota tersebut berbicara dengan nada merendahkan. Masyarakat terlihat tidak nyaman. Hal ini mencerminkan pelanggaran kode etik. (1)\",\"Saya melihat anggota menggunakan bahasa yang tidak sopan saat bertugas. Anggota tersebut berbicara dengan nada merendahkan. Masyarakat terlihat tidak nyaman. Hal ini mencerminkan pelanggaran kode etik. (2)\",\"Saya melihat anggota menggunakan bahasa yang tidak sopan saat bertugas. Anggota tersebut berbicara dengan nada merendahkan. Masyarakat terlihat tidak nyaman. Hal ini mencerminkan pelanggaran kode etik. (3)\"],[\"Harus di tindak untuk kasus ini\"],null,null,1778167344116,\"R/LI-2026050700074/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700074-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700075\",\"Infosus\",\"Saya melihat anggota berbicara dengan nada tinggi di tempat umum. Anggota tersebut terlihat emosional saat berinteraksi. Beberapa orang di sekitar merasa terganggu. Hal ini mencerminkan kurangnya pengendalian diri.\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"Saya melihat anggota berbicara dengan nada tinggi di tempat umum. Anggota tersebut terlihat emosional saat berinteraksi. Beberapa orang di sekitar merasa terganggu. Hal ini mencerminkan kurangnya pengendalian diri. (1)\",\"Saya melihat anggota berbicara dengan nada tinggi di tempat umum. Anggota tersebut terlihat emosional saat berinteraksi. Beberapa orang di sekitar merasa terganggu. Hal ini mencerminkan kurangnya pengendalian diri. (2)\",\"Saya melihat anggota berbicara dengan nada tinggi di tempat umum. Anggota tersebut terlihat emosional saat berinteraksi. Beberapa orang di sekitar merasa terganggu. Hal ini mencerminkan kurangnya pengendalian diri. (3)\"],null,[\"test_adhi\"],[\"Terganggu dengan kegiatan tersebut\"],1778167431071,\"R/Infosus - 2026050700075/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700075-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700076\",\"LI\",\"Saya datang untuk mengurus perpanjangan SIM. Namun petugas mengarahkan saya ke jalur cepat dengan biaya tambahan. Saya melihat beberapa orang lain juga diarahkan dengan cara yang sama. Hal ini membuat saya curiga adanya pungutan liar.\",\"test_pohan\",\"ormas jkl\",\"EO\",\"berbicara langsung\",\"medan tanggal 05 mei jam 13.00\",\"pungli\",[\"Saya datang untuk mengurus perpanjangan SIM. Namun petugas mengarahkan saya ke jalur cepat dengan biaya tambahan. Saya melihat beberapa orang lain juga diarahkan dengan cara yang sama. Hal ini membuat saya curiga adanya pungutan liar. (1)\",\"Saya datang untuk mengurus perpanjangan SIM. Namun petugas mengarahkan saya ke jalur cepat dengan biaya tambahan. Saya melihat beberapa orang lain juga diarahkan dengan cara yang sama. Hal ini membuat saya curiga adanya pungutan liar. (2)\"],[\"Pelaku atau anggota sudah ditemukan\"],null,null,1778167614684,\"R/LI-2026050700076/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700076-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700077\",\"Infosus\",\"Saya datang untuk melaporkan kehilangan barang berharga. Namun laporan saya tidak segera diproses oleh petugas. Saya diminta menunggu tanpa penjelasan yang jelas. Hal ini membuat saya merasa tidak mendapatkan pelayanan yang semestinya.\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"2 anggota terlihat santai dan saat datang sedang tidur\",\"proses hanya diketik dan tidak ada informasi yang jelas untuk saya menanyakan hal yang lebih detail untuk penanganan\"],null,[\"test_jovan\"],[\"Lanjut pemeriksaan\"],1778167720090,\"R/Infosus - 2026050700077/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700077-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700078\",\"LI\",\"Saya mengurus dokumen di kantor pelayanan. Proses berjalan sangat lama tanpa alasan yang jelas. Tidak ada informasi terkait keterlambatan tersebut. Hal ini membuat saya merasa dirugikan.\",\"Test_Bima\",\"Politrak\",\"Bpoliman\",\"Melihat jelas\",\"Senin sampai Jumat dengan paliman\",\"dispilin\",[\"Hari Weekday dikisaran jam 16-19\",\"tidur jam siang\"],[\"lanjut perkara\"],null,null,1778168163298,\"R/LI-2026050700078/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700078-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700079\",\"Infosus\",\"Saya melihat adanya interaksi antara petugas dan pengendara di jalan raya. Terlihat adanya pemberian uang secara langsung. Setelah itu pengendara tersebut diperbolehkan melanjutkan perjalanan. Hal ini menimbulkan dugaan pelanggaran.\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"Pungli secara langsung setiap kendaraan lewat\",\"terdapat 10 kendaran yang menjadi korban\"],null,[\"test_hari\"],[\"biar tidak berlarut langsung pemeriksaan\"],1778168272601,\"R/Infosus - 2026050700079/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700079-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700080\",\"LI\",\"Saya melihat razia kendaraan di jalan utama. Beberapa kendaraan diperiksa oleh petugas. Namun ada kendaraan yang dilepaskan setelah memberikan uang. Hal ini menimbulkan ketidakadilan.\",\"test_boomaan\",\"Pengusaha\",\"tidak ada\",\"melihat secara langsung\",\"Jalan simatupang setiap hari jam 07.30\",\"sandi pungli\",[\"kendaraan mobil dan motor\",\"setiap kendaraan motor yang sendirian\",\"korban mencapai kurang lebih 50 \"],[\"lanjut pemeriksaan dan investigasi\"],null,null,1778168448568,\"R/LI-2026050700080/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700080-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050700081\",\"Infosus\",\"Saya melihat anggota tidak menghargai masyarakat yang sedang berbicara. Anggota tersebut memotong pembicaraan dan bersikap tidak sabar. Masyarakat terlihat kecewa dengan sikap tersebut. Hal ini mencerminkan kurangnya etika komunikasi.\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"laporan asli dari penyelengaraan \",\"arogansi anggota\"],null,[\"OKe lanjut\"],[\"kebanyakan anggota yang baru lulus\"],1778169678500,\"R/Infosus - 2026050700081/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050700081-00001\",\"7 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050800001\",\"LI\",\"Pelapor melaporkan adanya dugaan punglian (pungutan liar) yang dilakukan oleh anggota polisi selama konser di Jawa Barat. Sekitar 1.000 orang diminta membayar pungutan Rp5.000 per orang, sehingga total pengumpulan uang mencapai Rp5.000.000. Pelapor menuntut penanganan dan pemeriksaan lebih lanjut atas perbuatan tersebut.\",\"Jasmien Koesnaryo\",\"Staff\",\"Staff\",\"Informasi langsung dari masyarakat dan staff lain yang bertugas \",\"Bandung, 2 mei 2026 \",\"1234\",[\"Ada 1000 orang yang dimintai pungutan liar \",\"Masing-masing dari orang yang menghadiri konser dimintai uang sebesar Rp 5.000 \",\"Total pengumpulan uang mencapai Rp5.000.000\"],[\"penanganan dan pemeriksaan lebih lanjut atas perbuatan tersebut\",\"tindakan tersebut menyalahi kode etik profesi polri \"],null,null,1778185622948,\"R/LI-2026050800001/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800001-00001\",\"8 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050800002\",\"Infosus\",\"Saya dijemput paksa tim buser pimpinan Ipda K. Barus. Di mobil saya dipukul supaya ngaku bandar narkoba. Pas di kantor ternyata NIK saya beda sama target. Saya dilepas gitu aja tanpa permintaan maaf, padahal muka saya sudah lebam.\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"Pelapor mengaku dijemput paksa oleh tim buser yang dipimpin Ipda K. Barus terkait dugaan kasus narkoba.\",\"Selama berada di dalam mobil, pelapor mengaku mengalami pemukulan agar mengakui sebagai bandar narkoba.\",\"Setelah tiba di kantor, diketahui bahwa NIK pelapor tidak sesuai dengan target yang dicari, kemudian pelapor dilepaskan tanpa permintaan maaf meskipun mengalami lebam pada wajah.\"],null,[\"Tanda tangan 1\",\"Tanda tangan 2\",\"Tanda tangan 3\"],[\"Perlu dilakukan verifikasi terkait prosedur penjemputan dan identitas target yang dicari oleh tim buser.\",\"Dugaan adanya tindakan kekerasan fisik selama proses penjemputan perlu didalami melalui pemeriksaan saksi, visum, maupun bukti pendukung lainnya.\",\"Perlu klarifikasi dari pihak terkait mengenai alasan pelepasan pelapor setelah diketahui terjadi kesalahan identifikasi.\"],1778185960645,\"R/Infosus - 2026050800002/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800002-00001\",\"8 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050800003\",\"Infosus\",\"Saya dijemput paksa tim buser pimpinan Ipda K. Barus. Di mobil saya dipukul supaya ngaku bandar narkoba. Pas di kantor ternyata NIK saya beda sama target. Saya dilepas gitu aja tanpa permintaan maaf, padahal muka saya sudah lebam.\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"Pelapor mengaku dijemput paksa oleh tim buser yang dipimpin Ipda K. Barus terkait dugaan kasus narkoba.\",\"Pelapor mengaku mengalami pemukulan di dalam mobil agar mengakui sebagai bandar narkoba\",\"Setelah dilakukan pengecekan, diketahui NIK pelapor tidak sesuai dengan target yang dicari dan pelapor kemudian dilepaskan tanpa permintaan maaf meskipun mengalami lebam pada wajah.\"],null,[\"Tanda tangan 1\",\"Tanda tangan 2\",\"Tanda tangan 3\"],[\"Perlu dilakukan verifikasi terkait prosedur penjemputan dan identitas target yang dicari oleh tim buser.\",\"Dugaan adanya tindakan kekerasan fisik selama proses penjemputan perlu didalami melalui pemeriksaan saksi, visum, maupun bukti pendukung lainnya.\",\"Perlu klarifikasi dari pihak terkait mengenai alasan pelepasan pelapor setelah diketahui terjadi kesalahan identifikasi.\"],1778186173219,\"R/Infosus - 2026050800003/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800003-00001\",\"8 Mei 2026\",\"SUBBID PAMINAL\",\"POLDA\",\"SUMATERA SELATAN\",\"\"],[\"2026050800004\",\"Infosus\",\"DUGAAN ANGGOTA POLRES KARANGANYAR TERLIBAT DALAM PENYALAHGUNAAN NARKOBA DI WILAYAH HUKUM POLDA JATENG\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"Bahwa pada hari Selasa tanggal 10 Februari 2026 Subbid Paminal Bidpropam Polda Jateng melaksanakan mitigasi kepada anggota Polres Karanganyar dengan sasaran diduga penyalahgunaan narkoba.\",\"Dalam melaksanakan Mitigasi kepada anggota Polres Karanganyar dengan sasaran diduga penyalahgunaan narkoba, Subbid Paminal Bidpropam Polda Jateng memanggil  anggota dengan identitas :\\nAiptu Heru Suwondo Nrp 72070638 Jabatan PS. KSPKT II Polsek Colomadu;\\nAiptu Purbo Wahyono Nrp 75040160 Jabatan PS. KSPKT I Polsek Colomadu;\\nAiptu Cucuk Kurniawan Nrp 76030021 Jabatan PS. Kanit Samapta Polsek Tasikmadu;\\n\",\"Dari ke 4 (empat) anggota Polres Karanganyar yang diduga melakukan penyalahgunaan Narkoba sewaktu dipanggil oleh Tim Mitigasi dari Subbid Paminal Bidpropam Polda Jateng untuk datang ke Polres Karanganyar tidak menghadiri panggilan dengan beralasan sakit maupun ada kepentingan keluarga.\"],null,[\"SYARIFUDIN\"],[\"Berkaitan dengan adanya informasi yang didapat bahwa ada anggota yang diduga melakukan penyalahgunaan Narkoba agar dilaksanakan pengecekan/ Test Urine.\"],1778186600802,\"R/Infosus - 2026050800004/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800004-00001\",\"8 Mei 2026\",\"SUBBID PAMINAL\",\"POLDA\",\"SUMATERA SELATAN\",\"\"],[\"2026050800004\",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,1778186770045,\"R/Infosus-2026050800004-00002/V/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800004-00002\",\"8 Mei 2026\",\"SUBBID PAMINAL\",\"POLDA\",\"SUMATERA SELATAN\",\"\"],[\"2026050800004\",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,1778186772397,\"R/Infosus-2026050800004-00003/V/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800004-00003\",\"8 Mei 2026\",\"SUBBID PAMINAL\",\"POLDA\",\"SUMATERA SELATAN\",\"\"],[\"2026050800005\",\"Infosus\",\"Pelapor melaporkan adanya dugaan punglian (pungutan liar) yang dilakukan oleh anggota polisi selama konser di Jawa Barat. Sekitar 1.000 orang diminta membayar pungutan Rp5.000 per orang, sehingga total pengumpulan uang mencapai Rp5.000.000. Pelapor menuntut penanganan dan pemeriksaan lebih lanjut atas perbuatan tersebut.\",null,null,null,null,null,null,[\"Sekitar 1.000 orang diminta membayar pungutan Rp5.000 per orang, sehingga total pengumpulan uang mencapai Rp5.000.000. \",\"Pelapor melaporkan adanya dugaan punglian (pungutan liar) yang dilakukan oleh anggota polisi selama konser di Jawa Barat. \"],null,[\"Irawan setyono\"],[\"tolong diproses lebih lanjut \"],1778186788257,\"R/Infosus - 2026050800005/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800005-00001\",\"8 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"],[\"2026050800006\",\"LI\",\"Saya dilaporkan karena masalah arisan online. Penyidik Aiptu B. Tambunan nakut-nakutin saya pakai pasal TPPU dan ancaman 10 tahun penjara. Beliau bilang kasus bisa 'aman' kalau saya bayar 40 juta. Saya stres dan merasa diperas padahal saya juga korban di arisan itu.\",\"TEST-SURYO\",\"Pramuniaga\",\"Rekan kerja\",\"Langsung\",\"Jakarta, 8 Januari 2026\",\"Pentolll\",[\"Pelapor mengaku dilaporkan terkait permasalahan arisan online.\",\"Pelapor menyebut penyidik Aiptu B. Tambunan mengancam menggunakan pasal TPPU dengan ancaman hukuman 10 tahun penjara.\",\"Pelapor mengaku merasa ditakut-takuti selama proses penanganan perkara.\",\"Pelapor menyatakan bahwa penyidik menyampaikan perkara dapat “aman” apabila memberikan uang sebesar Rp40 juta.\",\"Pelapor mengaku mengalami stres dan merasa menjadi korban pemerasan, serta menyatakan dirinya juga merupakan korban dalam kasus arisan online tersebut.\"],[\"Pelapor merasa proses penanganan perkara tidak dilakukan secara profesional karena adanya dugaan intimidasi dalam pemeriksaan.\",\"Pelapor berpendapat ancaman penggunaan pasal TPPU membuat dirinya berada dalam tekanan psikologis yang berat.\",\"Pelapor merasa permintaan uang sebesar Rp40 juta merupakan bentuk penyalahgunaan kewenangan.\",\"Pelapor menilai dirinya tidak diperlakukan secara adil karena mengaku juga menjadi korban dalam kasus arisan online tersebut.\",\"Pelapor berharap adanya pemeriksaan terhadap oknum penyidik terkait dugaan intimidasi dan permintaan sejumlah uang dalam penanganan perkara.\"],null,null,1778187173723,\"R/LI-2026050800006/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800006-00001\",\"8 Mei 2026\",\"SUBBID PAMINAL\",\"POLDA\",\"SUMATERA SELATAN\",\"\"],[\"2026050800008\",\"LI\",\"Dugaan pelanggaran disiplin yang dilakukan oleh \\nterduga pelangar A.n Aipda Syamsuddin Nrp. \\n83051257 Jabatan Ba Polres Bima yang diduga tidak \\npernah masuk kantor selama 28 (Dua puluh delapan) \\nHari  Hari Kerja secara tidak berturut-turut;\",\"ADDY SYACHABUDDIN.CH\",\"POLISI\",\"Teman Sejawat\",\"Kejadian Di Depan Mata\",\"Mapolres Bima; sejak tanggal 12 Desember 2025 sampai dengan   31 Januari 2026\",\"Sandi morse\",[\"tidak masuk kantor tanpa keterangan (TK) 28 (Dua \\npuluh delapan) Hari Hari Kerja secara tidak berturut\\nturut terhitung pada tanggal 12,13,15,16,17,18,19, 20, \\n22, 27, 29, 30 Desember 2025 dan pada tanggal \\n3,5,6,7,8,9,10,12,13,17,19,24,26,27,29,31 \\n2026.\"],[\"jahat dia\"],null,null,1778202836954,\"R/LI-2026050800008/IV/2026/Ropaminal\",\"2026050800008-00001\",\"8 Mei 2026\",null,null,\"\",\"\"]],\"developer\":{\"enabledReact\":true,\"enabled\":false,\"css\":\".card-ubahdata {\\n  display: flex;\\n  padding: 6px 12px 6px 8px;\\n  justify-content: center;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 8px;\\n  border-radius: 8px;\\n  border: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n  background: var(--white);\\n}\",\"js\":\"\",\"react\":\"import React, { useState, useEffect, useMemo } from 'react';\\nimport { useForm, Controller } from 'react-hook-form';\\nimport { Modal, Form, Row, Col, Button, InputGroup } from 'react-bootstrap';\\nimport styled from 'styled-components';\\nimport { DatePicker, TimePicker } from 'antd';\\nimport Select, { components } from 'react-select';\\nimport dayjs from 'dayjs';\\nimport axios from 'axios';\\nimport { dashboard } from '@store/app';\\n\\n// Dummy data untuk Laporan Informasi\\n// const dummyLaporanInformasiData = {\\n//   id: 'dummy-laporan-informasi-001',\\n//   status: 'Masuk',\\n//   created_date: '2026-03-03',\\n//   type_of_violation: 'Laporan Informasi',\\n\\n//   // DATA TERLAPOR\\n//   prepetrator_name: 'Bripka Doni Sutrisno',\\n//   rank: 'BRIPKA',\\n//   identity_number: '198505121990031001',\\n//   position: 'Kaur Ops',\\n//   report_date: '2026-03-11',\\n//   report_time: '10:30',\\n//   functional_assignment: 'Polres Jakarta Timur',\\n\\n//   // DATA PELANGGARAN - STEP 1\\n//   description:\\n//     'Melakukan penyalahgunaan wewenang dalam penanganan kasus - terjadi pada 01 Maret 2026 pukul 09:00 sambil ada pengawasan dari atasan',\\n\\n//   // DATA PELANGGARAN - STEP 2\\n//   chronology: [\\n//     {\\n//       description:\\n//         'Tanggal 01-03-2026 pukul 09:00, sambil ada pengawasan dari atasan',\\n//     },\\n//     {\\n//       description:\\n//         'Dilakukan pelanggaran sesuai dengan pasal yang telah dipilih secara sengaja dan melawan hukum',\\n//     },\\n//   ],\\n\\n//   // DATA PENANGGUNG JAWAB - STEP 3 (LAPORAN INFORMASI)\\n//   sender_name: 'Aiptu Suharto',\\n//   sender_rank: 'AIPTU',\\n//   sender_identity_number: '198705121990031002',\\n//   sender_unit: 'Polres Jakarta Timur',\\n\\n//   auditor_name: 'Ipda Bambang Hermawan',\\n//   auditor_rank: 'IPDA',\\n//   auditor_identity_number: '198605121990031003',\\n//   auditor_unit: 'Sat Propam Polres Jakarta Timur',\\n\\n//   know_name: 'Aipda Muhammad Yunus',\\n//   know_rank: 'AIPDA',\\n//   know_identity_number: '198805121990031004',\\n//   know_unit: 'Direktorat Propam Polda Metro Jaya',\\n\\n//   attachments: [],\\n// };\\n\\n// Dummy data untuk Infosus\\n// const dummyInfosusData = {\\n//   id: 'dummy-Infosus-001',\\n//   status: 'Masuk',\\n//   created_date: '2026-03-03',\\n//   type_of_violation: 'Infosus',\\n\\n//   // DATA TERLAPOR\\n//   prepetrator_name: 'Joni Hermawan, SE',\\n//   rank: 'JF2',\\n//   identity_number: '198705121990031005',\\n//   position: 'Kepala Bagian Administrasi',\\n//   report_time: '14:00',\\n//   report_date: '2026-03-15',\\n//   functional_assignment: 'Dinas Administrasi',\\n\\n//   // DATA PELANGGARAN - STEP 1\\n//   description:\\n//     'Terlambat masuk kerja secara berulang kali tanpa surat izin - tercatat minimal 15 kali dalam tiga bulan terakhir',\\n\\n//   // DATA PELANGGARAN - STEP 2\\n//   witnesses: [\\n//     { name: 'Endang Suryandari', position: 'Kepala Subbag Tata Usaha' },\\n//     { name: 'Fitri Handayani', position: 'Staff Administrasi' },\\n//   ],\\n//   evidence: [\\n//     { name: 'Absensi Bulan Februari 2026', type: 'Dokumen' },\\n//     { name: 'Surat Teguran Tertulis Nomor 001/2026', type: 'Dokumen' },\\n//   ],\\n//   kategori: 'Pelanggaran Disiplin',\\n//   sub_kategori: 'Keterlambatan Berulang',\\n//   wujud_perbuatan: 'Peraturan Disiplin',\\n\\n//   // DATA PENANGGUNG JAWAB - STEP 3 (INFOSUS)\\n//   creator_name: 'Siti Nurhaliza, SH',\\n//   creator_rank: 'JF1',\\n//   creator_identity_number: '198905121990031006',\\n//   creator_unit: 'Bagian Kepegawaian dan Organisasi',\\n\\n//   reviewer_name: 'Dr. Hendra Wijaya, MM',\\n//   reviewer_rank: 'JF3',\\n//   reviewer_identity_number: '198505121990031007',\\n//   reviewer_unit: 'Inspektorat Polda Metro Jaya',\\n\\n//   attachments: [],\\n// };\\n\\n// useEffect(() => {\\n//   const data = dummyLaporanInformasiData;\\n\\n//   reset(data);\\n// }, []);\\n\\n// const dummyData = [dummyLaporanInformasiData];\\n\\n// Komponen InfoDisplay untuk menampilkan informasi laporan\\nconst InfoDisplay = ({ report, type }) => {\\n  if (!report) return null;\\n\\n  const isInfosus = type === 'Infosus' || report?.report_type === 'Infosus';\\n  const getPendahuluanData = () => {\\n    // Laporan Informasi\\n    return [\\n      { label: 'Nama', value: report?.name || 'Pelapor' },\\n      { label: 'Pekerjaan', value: report?.occupation || 'Pengguna Layanan' },\\n      {\\n        label: 'Hubungan Dengan Sasaran',\\n        value: report?.relation_to_target || 'Korban',\\n      },\\n      {\\n        label: 'Cara Mendapatkan Baket',\\n        value: report?.information_source || 'Diberikan langsung',\\n      },\\n      {\\n        label: 'Tempat & Waktu Mendapatkan Baket',\\n        value:\\n          report?.information_place_time ||\\n          `${report?.functional_assignment || 'Polres'}, ${report?.report_date || '-'}`,\\n      },\\n    ];\\n  };\\n\\n  const getInfosusIntroData = () => {\\n    return [\\n      {\\n        label: 'Nama',\\n        value: report?.prepetrator_name || report?.name || '-',\\n      },\\n      {\\n        label: 'Pekerjaan',\\n        value: report?.position || report?.occupation || '-',\\n      },\\n      {\\n        label: 'Hubungan Dengan Sasaran',\\n        value: report?.relation_to_target || 'Tidak ada',\\n      },\\n      {\\n        label: 'Cara Mendapatkan Informasi',\\n        value: report?.information_source || '-',\\n      },\\n      {\\n        label: 'Tempat & Waktu Mendapatkan Informasi',\\n        value:\\n          report?.information_place_time ||\\n          `${report?.functional_assignment || '-'}, ${report?.report_date || '-'}`,\\n      },\\n    ];\\n  };\\n\\n  const getFaktaData = () => {\\n    if (\\n      report?.facts &&\\n      Array.isArray(report.facts) &&\\n      report.facts.length > 0\\n    ) {\\n      return report.facts.map((f) =>\\n        typeof f === 'object' ? f.facts || f.description || '' : f,\\n      );\\n    }\\n    if (report?.chronology && Array.isArray(report.chronology)) {\\n      return report.chronology.map((c) => c.description);\\n    }\\n    return [`${report?.description || report?.about || 'Tidak ada deskripsi'}`];\\n  };\\n\\n  const getPendapatData = () => {\\n    if (\\n      report?.reporter_opinion &&\\n      Array.isArray(report.reporter_opinion) &&\\n      report.reporter_opinion.length > 0\\n    ) {\\n      return report.reporter_opinion.map((o) =>\\n        typeof o === 'object' ? o.suggestion || o.description || '' : o,\\n      );\\n    }\\n    return [\\n      `${report?.description || report?.about || 'Tidak ada pendapat yang dicatat'}`,\\n    ];\\n  };\\n\\n  const getNotesData = () => {\\n    if (\\n      report?.notes &&\\n      Array.isArray(report.notes) &&\\n      report.notes.length > 0\\n    ) {\\n      return report.notes.map((o) =>\\n        typeof o === 'object' ? o.notes || '' : o,\\n      );\\n    }\\n    return [`${report?.notes || 'Tidak ada pendapat yang dicatat'}`];\\n  };\\n\\n  const parseArrayData = (data, fallbackKey = 'description') => {\\n    if (!data || !Array.isArray(data) || data.length === 0) return [];\\n    return data.map((item) =>\\n      typeof item === 'object'\\n        ? item[fallbackKey] || item.notes || item.suggestion || ''\\n        : item,\\n    );\\n  };\\n\\n  // Data sections berdasarkan tipe\\n  const sections = isInfosus\\n    ? [\\n        // 1. Perihal\\n        {\\n          title: 'Perihal',\\n          content: (\\n            <InfoText>\\n              {report?.about ||\\n                report?.description ||\\n                'Deskripsi tidak tersedia'}\\n            </InfoText>\\n          ),\\n        },\\n        // 2. Fakta-Fakta\\n        {\\n          title: 'Fakta-Fakta',\\n          content:\\n            parseArrayData(report?.facts, 'facts').length > 0\\n              ? parseArrayData(report.facts, 'facts')\\n              : parseArrayData(report?.chronology, 'description'),\\n          isList: true,\\n        },\\n        // 3. Catatan\\n        {\\n          title: 'Catatan',\\n          content:\\n            parseArrayData(report?.notes, 'notes').length > 0\\n              ? parseArrayData(report.notes, 'notes')\\n              : [report?.notes || 'Tidak ada catatan'],\\n          isList: true,\\n        },\\n        // 4. Paraf\\n        {\\n          title: 'Paraf',\\n          content:\\n            parseArrayData(report?.signature, 'signature').length > 0\\n              ? parseArrayData(report.signature, 'signature')\\n              : [\\n                  report?.signature ||\\n                    report?.paraph ||\\n                    'Tidak ada Tanda Tangan',\\n                ],\\n          isSignature: true,\\n          isList: true,\\n        },\\n      ]\\n    : [\\n        // 1. Tentang\\n        {\\n          title: 'Tentang',\\n          content: (\\n            <InfoText>\\n              {report?.about ||\\n                report?.description ||\\n                'Deskripsi laporan tidak tersedia'}\\n            </InfoText>\\n          ),\\n        },\\n        // 2. Pendahuluan\\n        {\\n          title: 'Pendahuluan',\\n          content: getPendahuluanData(),\\n          isFormList: true,\\n        },\\n        // 3. Fakta-Fakta\\n        {\\n          title: 'Fakta-Fakta',\\n          content:\\n            parseArrayData(report?.facts, 'facts').length > 0\\n              ? parseArrayData(report.facts, 'facts')\\n              : [report?.description || report?.about || 'Tidak ada deskripsi'],\\n          isList: true,\\n        },\\n        // 4. Pendapat Pelapor\\n        {\\n          title: 'Pendapat Pelapor',\\n          content:\\n            parseArrayData(report?.reporter_opinion, 'suggestion').length > 0\\n              ? parseArrayData(report.reporter_opinion, 'suggestion')\\n              : ['Tidak ada pendapat yang dicatat'],\\n          isList: true,\\n        },\\n        // 5. Pelapor -> Sandi\\n        {\\n          title: 'Pelapor',\\n          content: (\\n            <InfoListItem>\\n              <InfoLabel>Sandi</InfoLabel>\\n              <InfoValue>\\n                {report?.reporter_code || report?.sender_name || 'Anonim'}\\n              </InfoValue>\\n            </InfoListItem>\\n          ),\\n        },\\n      ];\\n\\n  // Renderer untuk content section\\n  const renderContent = (section) => {\\n    if (section.isSignature && Array.isArray(section.content)) {\\n      return (\\n        <SignatureBox>\\n          {section.content.map((item, idx) => (\\n            <InfoListItem key={idx}>\\n              <InfoText style={{ display: 'flex' }}>\\n                {section.content.length > 1 && (\\n                  <span style={{ marginRight: '8px' }}>{idx + 1}.</span>\\n                )}\\n                <span>{item}</span>\\n              </InfoText>\\n            </InfoListItem>\\n          ))}\\n        </SignatureBox>\\n      );\\n    }\\n    if (section.isFormList) {\\n      return section.content.map((item, idx) => (\\n        <InfoListItem key={idx}>\\n          <InfoLabel>{item.label}</InfoLabel>\\n          <InfoValue>{item.value}</InfoValue>\\n        </InfoListItem>\\n      ));\\n    }\\n    if (section.isList) {\\n      return section.content.map((item, idx) => (\\n        <InfoListItem key={idx}>\\n          <InfoText style={{ display: 'flex' }}>\\n            {section.content.length > 1 && (\\n              <span style={{ marginRight: '8px' }}>{idx + 1}.</span>\\n            )}\\n            <span>{item}</span>\\n          </InfoText>\\n        </InfoListItem>\\n      ));\\n    }\\n    return section.content;\\n  };\\n\\n  const pendahuluanData = getPendahuluanData();\\n  const faktaData = getFaktaData();\\n  const pendapatData = getPendapatData();\\n  const notesData = getNotesData();\\n\\n  return (\\n    <InfoDisplayContainer>\\n      {/* Tipe Laporan */}\\n      <InfoRow>\\n        <InfoLabel>Tipe Laporan</InfoLabel>\\n        <InfoValue>\\n          {report?.type_of_violation || report?.report_type || 'Informasi'}\\n        </InfoValue>\\n      </InfoRow>\\n\\n      <InfoDivider />\\n\\n      {/* Render sections dinamis */}\\n      {sections.map((section, idx) => (\\n        <div key={idx}>\\n          <InfoSection>\\n            <InfoSectionTitle>{section.title}</InfoSectionTitle>\\n            {renderContent(section)}\\n          </InfoSection>\\n          {idx < sections.length - 1 && (\\n            <InfoDivider style={{ marginTop: '1rem' }} />\\n          )}\\n        </div>\\n      ))}\\n    </InfoDisplayContainer>\\n  );\\n};\\n\\nexport default function InformasiLaporan({ widget, data, G, pageState, user }) {\\n  const rawData = Array.isArray(data) ? data : data?.data || [];\\n  const activeData = rawData.length > 0 ? rawData : '';\\n\\n  // const [dummySelection, setDummySelection] = useState('Laporan Informasi');\\n\\n  // const getActiveDataForDummy = () => {\\n  //   if (data && data.length > 0) return data;\\n  //   return dummySelection === 'Infosus'\\n  //     ? [dummyInfosusData]\\n  //     : [dummyLaporanInformasiData];\\n  // };\\n\\n  // const activeData = getActiveDataForDummy();\\n  const [items, setItems] = useState(data || []);\\n  const [showModal, setShowModal] = useState<boolean>(false);\\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState('data-terlapor');\\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\\n  const [showValidationError, setShowValidationError] = useState(false);\\n\\n  const [isDragging, setIsDragging] = useState(false);\\n  const [files, setFiles] = useState([]);\\n\\n  const [uploadedFiles, setUploadedFiles] = useState([]);\\n  const report = activeData[0];\\n  const [step, setStep] = useState(1);\\n  const handleCloseWithReset = () => {\\n    setStep(1); // Reset ke step 1\\n    handleCloseEdit();\\n  };\\n\\n  const pages = {\\n    informasiDasar: pageState?.['dad5b834f5a7a46b8a119d6e54211dbd'],\\n  };\\n\\n  const informasiDasarData = pages.informasiDasar?.data?.[0] || {};\\n\\n  console.log('ini informasi data:', informasiDasarData);\\n\\n  console.log(report, 'ini report');\\n\\n  const {\\n    register,\\n    watch,\\n    control,\\n    formState: { errors },\\n  } = useForm();\\n\\n  const {\\n    register: registerEdit,\\n    handleSubmit: handleSubmitEdit,\\n    watch: watchEdit,\\n    setValue: setValueEdit,\\n    reset: resetEdit,\\n    trigger: triggerEdit,\\n    control: controlEdit,\\n    formState: { errors: errorsEdit },\\n  } = useForm({\\n    defaultValues: {\\n      // DATA TERLAPOR / PELAPOR\\n      prepetrator_name: report?.prepetrator_name || report?.name || '',\\n      // birth_place: report?.birth_place || '',\\n      report_date: report?.report_date || '',\\n      rank: report?.rank || '',\\n      identity_number: report?.identity_number || '',\\n      position: report?.position || report?.occupation || '',\\n      prepetrator_phone: report?.prepetrator_phone || '',\\n      report_time: report?.report_time || '',\\n      functional_assignment:\\n        report?.functional_assignment || report?.information_place_time || '',\\n\\n      // FORM FIELDS MAPPING\\n      about: report?.about || report?.description || '',\\n      name: report?.name || report?.sender_name || '',\\n      occupations: report?.occupation || report?.position || '',\\n      relation: report?.relation_to_target || '',\\n      get_baket: report?.information_source || '',\\n      get_baket_time: report?.information_place_time || '',\\n      password: report?.reporter_code || '',\\n      perihal: report?.about || report?.description || '',\\n      facts: (report?.facts || report?.chronology || []).map((f) => ({\\n        facts: typeof f === 'object' ? f.facts || f.description || '' : f,\\n      })),\\n      suggestion: (report?.reporter_opinion || []).map((o) => ({\\n        suggestion:\\n          typeof o === 'object' ? o.suggestion || o.description || '' : o,\\n      })),\\n      notes: (report?.notes || []).map((n) => ({\\n        notes: typeof n === 'object' ? n.notes || n.description || '' : n,\\n      })),\\n      sign: (report?.signature || []).map((s) => ({\\n        sign: typeof s === 'object' ? s.sign || s.description || '' : s,\\n      })),\\n\\n      // DATA PELANGGARAN\\n      description: report?.description || '',\\n      kategori: report?.kategori || '',\\n      sub_kategori: report?.sub_kategori || '',\\n      chronology: report?.chronology || [],\\n\\n      // DATA PENANGGUNG JAWAB - LAPORAN INFORMASI\\n      // Pembuat Laporan\\n      sender_name: report?.sender_name || '',\\n      sender_rank: report?.sender_rank || '',\\n      sender_identity_number: report?.sender_identity_number || '',\\n      sender_unit: report?.sender_unit || '',\\n\\n      // Pemeriksa\\n      auditor_name: report?.auditor_name || '',\\n      auditor_rank: report?.auditor_rank || '',\\n      auditor_identity_number: report?.auditor_identity_number || '',\\n      auditor_unit: report?.auditor_unit || '',\\n\\n      // Mengetahui\\n      know_name: report?.know_name || '',\\n      know_rank: report?.know_rank || '',\\n      know_identity_number: report?.know_identity_number || '',\\n      know_unit: report?.know_unit || '',\\n\\n      // DATA PENANGGUNG JAWAB - INFOSUS\\n      // Yang Membuat Laporan\\n      creator_name: report?.creator_name || '',\\n      creator_rank: report?.creator_rank || '',\\n      creator_identity_number: report?.creator_identity_number || '',\\n      creator_unit: report?.creator_unit || '',\\n\\n      // Mengetahui\\n      reviewer_name: report?.reviewer_name || '',\\n      reviewer_rank: report?.reviewer_rank || '',\\n      reviewer_identity_number: report?.reviewer_identity_number || '',\\n      reviewer_unit: report?.reviewer_unit || '',\\n\\n      // Witness & Evidence untuk Infosus\\n      witnesses: report?.witnesses || [],\\n      evidence: report?.evidence || [],\\n\\n      // ID\\n      id: report?.id || '',\\n    },\\n    mode: 'onChange',\\n  });\\n\\n  const selectedTipeLaporan = report?.report_type || 'LI';\\n  const maxStep = 3;\\n\\n  const handleOpenEdit = () => {\\n    resetEdit({\\n      report_type: report?.report_type || '',\\n      perihal: report?.about || report?.description || '',\\n      about: report?.about || report?.description || '',\\n      name: report?.name || report?.sender_name || '',\\n      occupations: report?.occupation || report?.position || '',\\n      relation: report?.relation_to_target || '',\\n      get_baket: report?.information_source || '',\\n      get_baket_time: report?.information_place_time || '',\\n      password: report?.reporter_code || '',\\n\\n      facts: (report?.facts || []).map((f) => ({\\n        facts: typeof f === 'object' ? f.facts || f.description || '' : f,\\n      })),\\n\\n      suggestion: (report?.reporter_opinion || []).map((o) => ({\\n        suggestion:\\n          typeof o === 'object' ? o.suggestion || o.description || '' : o,\\n      })),\\n\\n      sign: (report?.signature || []).map((s) => ({\\n        sign: typeof s === 'object' ? s.sign || s.description || '' : s,\\n      })),\\n\\n      notes: (report?.notes || []).map((n) => ({\\n        notes: typeof n === 'object' ? n.notes || n.description || '' : n,\\n      })),\\n\\n      // ID\\n      id: report?.id || '',\\n    });\\n\\n    setShowModal(true);\\n  };\\n  const handleCloseEdit = () => {\\n    setShowModal(false);\\n    resetEdit();\\n  };\\n\\n  const onSubmitEdit = async (formData) => {\\n    console.log('=== SUBMIT EDIT ===');\\n    console.log('Step saat ini:', step);\\n    console.log('Form data:', formData);\\n\\n    setLoading(true);\\n\\n    try {\\n      if (selectedTipeLaporan === 'Laporan Informasi') {\\n        if (!formData.about) {\\n          alert('Tentang wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.name) {\\n          alert('Nama wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.occupations) {\\n          alert('Pekerjaan wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.relation) {\\n          alert('Hubungan Dengan Sasaran wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.get_baket) {\\n          alert('Cara Mendapat Baket wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.get_baket_time) {\\n          alert('Tempat & Waktu Mendapat Baket wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.facts) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Fakta wajib ditambahkan');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.suggestion) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Pendapat wajib ditambahkan');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.password) {\\n          alert('Sandi wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n      } else if (selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus') {\\n        if (!formData.perihal) {\\n          alert('Perihal wajib diisi');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.facts) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Fakta wajib ditambahkan');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.notes) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Catatan wajib ditambahkan');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n        if (!formData.sign) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Paraf wajib ditambahkan');\\n          setLoading(false);\\n          return;\\n        }\\n      }\\n\\n      const buildEditData = () => {\\n        const baseData = {\\n          id: report?.report_id,\\n        };\\n\\n        // Add report-type specific data\\n        if (selectedTipeLaporan === 'LI') {\\n          baseData.report_type = 'LI';\\n\\n          // Step 1\\n          if (formData.about) baseData.about = formData.about;\\n          if (formData.name) baseData.name = formData.name;\\n          if (formData.occupations) baseData.occupation = formData.occupations;\\n          if (formData.relation)\\n            baseData.relation_to_target = formData.relation;\\n          if (formData.get_baket)\\n            baseData.information_source = formData.get_baket;\\n          if (formData.get_baket_time)\\n            baseData.information_place_time = formData.get_baket_time;\\n\\n          // Step 2\\n          if (formData.facts && formData.facts.length > 0) {\\n            baseData.facts = formData.facts\\n              .map((f) => f.facts || f.description || '')\\n              .filter(Boolean);\\n          }\\n          if (formData.suggestion && formData.suggestion.length > 0) {\\n            baseData.reporter_opinion = formData.suggestion\\n              .map((s) => s.suggestion || s.description || '')\\n              .filter(Boolean);\\n          }\\n\\n          // Step 3\\n          if (formData.password) baseData.reporter_code = formData.password;\\n        } else if (selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus') {\\n          baseData.report_type = 'Infosus';\\n\\n          if (formData.perihal) baseData.about = formData.perihal;\\n\\n          if (formData.facts && formData.facts.length > 0) {\\n            baseData.facts = formData.facts\\n              .map((f) => f.facts || f.description || '')\\n              .filter(Boolean);\\n          }\\n          if (formData.notes && formData.notes.length > 0) {\\n            baseData.notes = formData.notes\\n              .map((n) => n.notes || n.description || '')\\n              .filter(Boolean);\\n          }\\n          if (formData.sign && formData.sign.length > 0) {\\n            baseData.signature = formData.sign\\n              .map((s) => s.sign || s.description || '')\\n              .filter(Boolean);\\n          }\\n        }\\n\\n        return baseData;\\n      };\\n\\n      const editData = buildEditData();\\n\\n      console.log('Edit payload:', editData);\\n      console.log('=== DEBUGGING INFO ===');\\n      console.log('Widget:', widget);\\n      console.log('PageState:', pageState);\\n      console.log('User:', user);\\n      console.log('User ID:', user?.id);\\n      console.log('Widget ID:', widget?.id);\\n      console.log('Widget Dashboard ID:', widget?.dashboardId);\\n      console.log('PageState Dashboard ID:', pageState?.dashboard?.id);\\n\\n      const requestPayload = {\\n        client: 'Propam Polri',\\n        gatewayId: 'e4e831724de91c15a04833cecaf581b3',\\n        params: editData,\\n        body: {},\\n        headers: {},\\n        additionalPath: '',\\n        additionalParams: {},\\n        additionalFileParams: {},\\n        tags: ['Propam Polri'],\\n        createdBy: user?.id || '',\\n        startDate: '',\\n        endDate: '',\\n        dashboardId: dashboard?.id || '',\\n        sessionId: '',\\n        logging: false,\\n        appendedLog: false,\\n      };\\n\\n      console.log('Sending to gateway:', requestPayload);\\n\\n      const gatewayResponse = await fetch('/api/v1/apps/api/gateway/execute', {\\n        method: 'POST',\\n        headers: {\\n          'Content-Type': 'application/json',\\n        },\\n        body: JSON.stringify(requestPayload),\\n      });\\n\\n      if (!gatewayResponse.ok) {\\n        const errorText = await gatewayResponse.text();\\n        throw new Error(\\n          `Gateway error: ${gatewayResponse.status} - ${errorText}`,\\n        );\\n      }\\n\\n      const gatewayResult = await gatewayResponse.json();\\n      console.log('Edit success:', gatewayResult);\\n\\n      if (typeof dispatchNotification === 'function') {\\n        dispatchNotification('Laporan berhasil diedit!', 'success');\\n      }\\n\\n      alert('Data laporan berhasil diperbarui!');\\n\\n      setShowModal(false);\\n      resetEdit();\\n      setStep(1);\\n      setFiles([]);\\n      setUploadedFiles([]);\\n    } catch (err) {\\n      console.error('Error editing laporan:', err);\\n\\n      // Notifikasi error\\n      if (typeof dispatchNotification === 'function') {\\n        dispatchNotification(`Error: ${err.message}`, 'danger');\\n      }\\n\\n      alert(`Gagal mengupdate data: ${err.message}`);\\n    } finally {\\n      setLoading(false);\\n    }\\n  };\\n\\n  // step validation\\n  const handleNext = async () => {\\n    let isValid = true;\\n\\n    if (selectedTipeLaporan === 'LI') {\\n      if (step === 1) {\\n        if (!watchEdit('about')) {\\n          alert('Tentang wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        } else if (!watchEdit('name')) {\\n          alert('Nama wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        } else if (!watchEdit('occupations')) {\\n          alert('Pekerjaan wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        } else if (!watchEdit('relation')) {\\n          alert('Hubungan Dengan Sasaran wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        } else if (!watchEdit('get_baket')) {\\n          alert('Cara Mendapat Baket wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        } else if (!watchEdit('get_baket_time')) {\\n          alert('Tempat & Waktu Mendapat Baket wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        }\\n      } else if (step === 2) {\\n        if (!watchEdit('facts') || watchEdit('facts').length === 0) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Fakta wajib ditambahkan');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        }\\n      } else if (step === 3) {\\n        if (!watchEdit('suggestion') || watchEdit('suggestion').length === 0) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Pendapat wajib ditambahkan');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        } else if (!watchEdit('password')) {\\n          alert('Sandi wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        }\\n      }\\n    } else if (selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus') {\\n      if (step === 1) {\\n        if (!watchEdit('perihal')) {\\n          alert('Perihal wajib diisi');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        } else if (!watchEdit('facts') || watchEdit('facts').length === 0) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Fakta wajib ditambahkan');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        }\\n      } else if (step === 2) {\\n        if (!watchEdit('notes') || watchEdit('notes').length === 0) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Catatan wajib ditambahkan');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        }\\n      } else if (step === 3) {\\n        if (!watchEdit('sign' || watchEdit(sign).length === 0)) {\\n          alert('Minimal 1 Paraf wajib ditambahkan');\\n          isValid = false;\\n        }\\n      }\\n    }\\n\\n    if (isValid && step < maxStep) {\\n      setStep(step + 1);\\n    }\\n  };\\n\\n  const handlePrevious = () => {\\n    if (step > 1) {\\n      setStep(step - 1);\\n    }\\n  };\\n  return (\\n    <>\\n      <div\\n        className=\\\"h-100\\\"\\n        style={{\\n          border: '1px solid var(--black-100)',\\n          borderRadius: '0.8rem',\\n          backgroundColor: 'var(--white)',\\n        }}\\n      >\\n        <div\\n          className=\\\"flex justify-between items-center\\\"\\n          style={{\\n            borderBottom: '1px solid var(--black-100)',\\n            padding: '16px 20px',\\n          }}\\n        >\\n          <div className=\\\"widget-title\\\">\\n            {widget?.name || 'Laporan Informasi atau Infosus'}\\n          </div>\\n          <div className=\\\"d-flex gap-2 align-items-center\\\">\\n            <div className=\\\"card-ubahdata\\\" onClick={handleOpenEdit}>\\n              <i class=\\\"ph ph-pencil-simple-line\\\"></i>\\n              <div> Ubah Data</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        {/* Body - Info Display */}\\n        <InfoDisplay report={report} type={selectedTipeLaporan} />\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <StyledModal centered size=\\\"lg\\\" show={showModal} onHide={handleCloseEdit}>\\n        <Form onSubmit={handleSubmitEdit(onSubmitEdit)}>\\n          <ModalHeader closeButton>\\n            <WrappIcon>\\n              <i\\n                className=\\\"ph-duotone ph-user\\\"\\n                style={{ fontSize: '1.6rem', color: 'var(--primary)' }}\\n              ></i>\\n            </WrappIcon>\\n            <div className=\\\"d-flex flex-column gap-1\\\">\\n              <TitleHeader>Laporan Informasi</TitleHeader>\\n              <DescHeader>Sesuaikan isi laporan</DescHeader>\\n            </div>\\n          </ModalHeader>\\n          <ModalBody>\\n            {step === 1 && (\\n              <TitleInput\\n                className=\\\"pb-2\\\"\\n                style={{ color: 'var(--black-600)', fontSize: '1.14286rem' }}\\n              >\\n                Data Laporan\\n              </TitleInput>\\n            )}\\n\\n            {step === 1 && (\\n              <div className=\\\"d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between gap-3 w-100\\\">\\n                {/* Kolom 1 */}\\n                <div\\n                  className=\\\"d-flex flex-column\\\"\\n                  style={{ width: '100%', maxWidth: '48%' }}\\n                >\\n                  <Form.Group className=\\\"d-flex flex-column gap-2 w-100\\\">\\n                    <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">\\n                      Tipe Laporan <span className=\\\"text-danger\\\">*</span>\\n                    </TitleInput>\\n\\n                    <div className=\\\"d-flex gap-2\\\">\\n                      <RadioButtonContainer\\n                        isSelected={selectedTipeLaporan === 'LI'}\\n                        onClick={() => {}}\\n                        type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                        disabled={true}\\n                        style={{\\n                          opacity: 0.6,\\n                          cursor: 'not-allowed',\\n                        }}\\n                      >\\n                        <FormCheckStyled\\n                          type=\\\"radio\\\"\\n                          checked={selectedTipeLaporan === 'LI'}\\n                          onChange={() => {}}\\n                          name=\\\"tipe-laporan\\\"\\n                          disabled={true}\\n                        />\\n                        <p>Laporan Informasi</p>\\n                      </RadioButtonContainer>\\n\\n                      <RadioButtonContainer\\n                        isSelected={selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus'}\\n                        onClick={() => {}}\\n                        type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                        disabled={true}\\n                        style={{\\n                          opacity: 0.6,\\n                          cursor: 'not-allowed',\\n                        }}\\n                      >\\n                        <FormCheckStyled\\n                          type=\\\"radio\\\"\\n                          checked={selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus'}\\n                          onChange={() => {}}\\n                          name=\\\"tipe-laporan\\\"\\n                          disabled={true}\\n                        />\\n                        <p>Infosus</p>\\n                      </RadioButtonContainer>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </Form.Group>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            )}\\n\\n            {step === 1 && selectedTipeLaporan === 'LI' && (\\n              <div className=\\\"d-flex flex-column w-100\\\">\\n                <Form.Group className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">Tentang</TitleInput>\\n                  <StyledTextarea\\n                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                    as={'textarea'}\\n                    rows={3}\\n                    placeholder=\\\"Tentang\\\"\\n                    {...registerEdit('about')}\\n                  />\\n                </Form.Group>\\n\\n                <Divinder />\\n                {/* <hr style={{ borderColor: 'var(--black-100)' }} /> */}\\n\\n                <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">Pendahuluan</TitleInput>\\n\\n                {/* Nama */}\\n                <FormStyle\\n                  className=\\\"w-100\\\"\\n                  style={{ marginBottom: '1.14rem' }}\\n                >\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">Nama</TitleInput>\\n                  <StyledInput\\n                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                    placeholder=\\\"Nama\\\"\\n                    {...registerEdit('name')}\\n                  />\\n                </FormStyle>\\n\\n                {/* Pekerjaan */}\\n                <FormStyle className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">Pekerjaan</TitleInput>\\n                  <StyledInput\\n                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                    placeholder=\\\"Pekerjaan\\\"\\n                    {...registerEdit('occupations')}\\n                  />\\n                </FormStyle>\\n\\n                {/* Hubungan dengan Sasaran */}\\n                <FormStyle className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">\\n                    Hubungan Dengan Sasaran\\n                  </TitleInput>\\n                  <StyledInput\\n                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                    placeholder=\\\"Hubungan Dengan Sasaran\\\"\\n                    {...registerEdit('relation')}\\n                  />\\n                </FormStyle>\\n\\n                {/* Cara Mendapat Baket */}\\n                <FormStyle className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">Cara Mendapat Baket</TitleInput>\\n                  <StyledInput\\n                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                    placeholder=\\\"Cara Mendapat Baket\\\"\\n                    {...registerEdit('get_baket')}\\n                  />\\n                </FormStyle>\\n\\n                {/* Tempat & Waktu Mendapatkan Baket */}\\n                <FormStyle className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">\\n                    Tempat & Waktu Mendapat Baket\\n                  </TitleInput>\\n                  <StyledInput\\n                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                    placeholder=\\\"Cara Mendapat Braket\\\"\\n                    {...registerEdit('get_baket_time')}\\n                  />\\n                </FormStyle>\\n              </div>\\n            )}\\n\\n            {/* STEP 1 - Infosus */}\\n            {step === 1 && selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus' && (\\n              <div className=\\\"d-flex flex-column gap-3 w-100\\\">\\n                {/* Perihal */}\\n                <Form.Group className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">Perihal</TitleInput>\\n                  <StyledTextarea\\n                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                    as={'textarea'}\\n                    rows={3}\\n                    placeholder=\\\"Isi perihal secara detail\\\"\\n                    {...registerEdit('perihal')}\\n                  />\\n                </Form.Group>\\n\\n                <Divinder />\\n                <Form.Group className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <div\\n                    className=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\\\"\\n                    style={{ marginBottom: '1.43rem' }}\\n                  >\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        fontSize: '1.14286rem',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Fakta-Fakta\\n                    </div>\\n                    <button\\n                      type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                      onClick={() => {\\n                        const current = watchEdit('facts') || [];\\n                        setValueEdit('facts', [...current, { facts: '' }]);\\n                      }}\\n                      style={{\\n                        background: 'none',\\n                        border: 'none',\\n                        color: 'var(--primary)',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        cursor: 'pointer',\\n                        padding: 0,\\n                        fontSize: '1rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      + Tambah Fakta\\n                    </button>\\n                  </div>\\n\\n                  {(watchEdit('facts') || []).length > 0 ? (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        display: 'flex',\\n                        flexDirection: 'column',\\n                        gap: '0.75rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      {(watchEdit('facts') || []).map((item, index) => (\\n                        <div\\n                          key={index}\\n                          style={{\\n                            width: '100%',\\n                            paddingTop: 11,\\n                            paddingBottom: 11,\\n                            paddingLeft: 16,\\n                            paddingRight: 11,\\n                            background: 'var(--Background-Primary, white)',\\n                            overflow: 'hidden',\\n                            borderRadius: 10,\\n                            outline: '1px var(--Border-Primary, #E6E9F0) solid',\\n                            outlineOffset: '-1px',\\n                            justifyContent: 'flex-start',\\n                            alignItems: 'flex-start',\\n                            gap: 8,\\n                            display: 'inline-flex',\\n                          }}\\n                        >\\n                          <CustomStyledTextarea\\n                            as=\\\"textarea\\\"\\n                            rows={2}\\n                            placeholder=\\\"Masukkan Fakta-Fakta\\\"\\n                            value={item.facts || ''}\\n                            onChange={(e) => {\\n                              const current = watchEdit('facts') || [];\\n                              const updated = current.map((item, i) =>\\n                                i === index\\n                                  ? { ...item, facts: e.target.value }\\n                                  : item,\\n                              );\\n                              setValueEdit('facts', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              flex: '1 1 0',\\n                            }}\\n                          />\\n                          <button\\n                            type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                            onClick={() => {\\n                              const updated = (watchEdit('facts') || []).filter(\\n                                (_, i) => i !== index,\\n                              );\\n                              setValueEdit('facts', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              width: 16,\\n                              justifyContent: 'flex-start',\\n                              alignItems: 'center',\\n                              gap: 10,\\n                              display: 'flex',\\n                              background: 'none',\\n                              border: 'none',\\n                              cursor: 'pointer',\\n                              padding: 0,\\n                              minWidth: 16,\\n                              flexShrink: 0,\\n                            }}\\n                          >\\n                            <i className=\\\"ph ph-x\\\" style={{ fontSize: 16 }}></i>\\n                          </button>\\n                        </div>\\n                      ))}\\n                    </div>\\n                  ) : (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        padding: '1rem',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        backgroundColor: 'var(--black-25)',\\n                        borderRadius: '0.5rem',\\n                        border: '1px dashed var(--black-100)',\\n                        fontSize: '1rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Belum ada Fakta-Fakta. Klik \\\"Tambah Fakta\\\" untuk\\n                      menambahkan.\\n                    </div>\\n                  )}\\n                </Form.Group>\\n              </div>\\n            )}\\n\\n            {/* STEP 2 - Laporan Informasi: Kronologi */}\\n            {step === 2 && selectedTipeLaporan === 'LI' && (\\n              <>\\n                <Form.Group className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <div\\n                    className=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\\\"\\n                    style={{ marginBottom: '1.43rem' }}\\n                  >\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        fontSize: '1.14286rem',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Fakta-Fakta\\n                    </div>\\n\\n                    <button\\n                      type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                      onClick={() => {\\n                        const current = watchEdit('facts') || [];\\n                        setValueEdit('facts', [...current, { facts: '' }]);\\n                      }}\\n                      style={{\\n                        background: 'none',\\n                        border: 'none',\\n                        color: 'var(--primary)',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        cursor: 'pointer',\\n                        padding: 0,\\n                        fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      + Tambah Fakta\\n                    </button>\\n                  </div>\\n\\n                  {(watchEdit('facts') || []).length > 0 ? (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        display: 'flex',\\n                        flexDirection: 'column',\\n                        gap: '0.75rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      {(watchEdit('facts') || []).map((item, index) => (\\n                        <div\\n                          key={index}\\n                          style={{\\n                            width: '100%',\\n                            paddingTop: 11,\\n                            paddingBottom: 11,\\n                            paddingLeft: 16,\\n                            paddingRight: 11,\\n                            background: 'var(--Background-Primary, white)',\\n                            overflow: 'hidden',\\n                            borderRadius: 10,\\n                            outline: '1px var(--Border-Primary, #E6E9F0) solid',\\n                            outlineOffset: '-1px',\\n                            justifyContent: 'flex-start',\\n                            alignItems: 'flex-start',\\n                            gap: 8,\\n                            display: 'inline-flex',\\n                          }}\\n                        >\\n                          <CustomStyledTextarea\\n                            as=\\\"textarea\\\"\\n                            rows={2}\\n                            placeholder=\\\"Masukkan Fakta-Fakta\\\"\\n                            value={item.facts || ''}\\n                            onChange={(e) => {\\n                              const current = watchEdit('facts') || [];\\n                              const updated = current.map((item, i) =>\\n                                i === index\\n                                  ? { ...item, facts: e.target.value }\\n                                  : item,\\n                              );\\n                              setValueEdit('facts', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              flex: '1 1 0',\\n                            }}\\n                          />\\n                          <button\\n                            type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                            onClick={() => {\\n                              const updated = (watchEdit('facts') || []).filter(\\n                                (_, i) => i !== index,\\n                              );\\n                              setValueEdit('facts', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              width: 16,\\n                              justifyContent: 'flex-start',\\n                              alignItems: 'center',\\n                              gap: 10,\\n                              display: 'flex',\\n                              background: 'none',\\n                              border: 'none',\\n                              cursor: 'pointer',\\n                              padding: 0,\\n                              minWidth: 16,\\n                              flexShrink: 0,\\n                            }}\\n                          >\\n                            <i className=\\\"ph ph-x\\\" style={{ fontSize: 16 }}></i>\\n                          </button>\\n                        </div>\\n                      ))}\\n                    </div>\\n                  ) : (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        padding: '1rem',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        backgroundColor: 'var(--black-25)',\\n                        borderRadius: '0.5rem',\\n                        border: '1px dashed var(--black-100)',\\n                        fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Belum ada Fakta. Klik \\\"Tambah Fakta\\\" untuk menambahkan.\\n                    </div>\\n                  )}\\n                </Form.Group>\\n              </>\\n            )}\\n\\n            {/* STEP 2 - Infosus: Catatan */}\\n            {step === 2 && selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus' && (\\n              <div className=\\\"d-flex flex-column gap-3 w-100\\\">\\n                {/* Catatan */}\\n                <Form.Group className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <div\\n                    className=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\\\"\\n                    style={{ marginBottom: '1.43rem' }}\\n                  >\\n                    {/* <LabelInput>Catatan</LabelInput> */}\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        fontSize: '1.14286rem',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Catatan\\n                    </div>\\n                    <button\\n                      type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                      onClick={() => {\\n                        const current = watchEdit('notes') || [];\\n                        setValueEdit('notes', [...current, { note: '' }]);\\n                      }}\\n                      style={{\\n                        background: 'none',\\n                        border: 'none',\\n                        color: 'var(--primary)',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        cursor: 'pointer',\\n                        padding: 0,\\n                        fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      + Tambah Catatan\\n                    </button>\\n                  </div>\\n                  {(watchEdit('notes') || []).length > 0 ? (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        display: 'flex',\\n                        flexDirection: 'column',\\n                        gap: '0.75rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      {(watchEdit('notes') || []).map((item, index) => (\\n                        <div\\n                          key={index}\\n                          style={{\\n                            width: '100%',\\n                            paddingLeft: 16,\\n                            paddingRight: 16,\\n                            paddingTop: 11,\\n                            paddingBottom: 11,\\n                            background: 'white',\\n                            overflow: 'hidden',\\n                            borderRadius: 10,\\n                            outline: '1px #E6E9F0 solid',\\n                            outlineOffset: '-1px',\\n                            justifyContent: 'space-between',\\n                            alignItems: 'center',\\n                            gap: 8,\\n                            display: 'flex',\\n                          }}\\n                        >\\n                          <input\\n                            type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                            placeholder=\\\"Masukkan catatan\\\"\\n                            value={item.notes || ''}\\n                            onChange={(e) => {\\n                              const current = watchEdit('notes') || [];\\n                              const updated = current.map((item, i) =>\\n                                i === index\\n                                  ? { ...item, notes: e.target.value }\\n                                  : item,\\n                              );\\n                              setValueEdit('notes', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              flex: '1 1 0',\\n                              color: item.notes ? '#050505' : '#A0A3AA',\\n                              fontSize: 14,\\n                              fontFamily: 'Inter',\\n                              fontWeight: '400',\\n                              lineHeight: '19.60px',\\n                              wordWrap: 'break-word',\\n                              border: 'none',\\n                              outline: 'none',\\n                              background: 'transparent',\\n                            }}\\n                          />\\n                          <button\\n                            type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                            onClick={() => {\\n                              const updated = (watchEdit('notes') || []).filter(\\n                                (_, i) => i !== index,\\n                              );\\n                              setValueEdit('notes', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              width: 16,\\n                              height: 16,\\n                              position: 'relative',\\n                              background: 'none',\\n                              border: 'none',\\n                              cursor: 'pointer',\\n                              padding: 0,\\n                              display: 'flex',\\n                              alignItems: 'center',\\n                              justifyContent: 'center',\\n                            }}\\n                          >\\n                            <i className=\\\"ph ph-x\\\" style={{ fontSize: 16 }} />\\n                          </button>\\n                        </div>\\n                      ))}\\n                    </div>\\n                  ) : (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        padding: '1rem',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        backgroundColor: 'var(--black-25)',\\n                        borderRadius: '0.5rem',\\n                        border: '1px dashed var(--black-100)',\\n                        fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Belum ada Catatan. Klik \\\"Tambah Catatan\\\" untuk\\n                      menambahkan.\\n                    </div>\\n                  )}\\n                </Form.Group>\\n              </div>\\n            )}\\n\\n            {/* STEP 3 - Laporan Informasi: Penanggung Jawab */}\\n            {step === 3 && selectedTipeLaporan === 'LI' && (\\n              <>\\n                <Form.Group className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                  <div\\n                    className=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\\\"\\n                    style={{ marginBottom: '1.43rem' }}\\n                  >\\n                    {/* <LabelInput>Pendapat Pelapor</LabelInput> */}\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        fontSize: '1.14286rem',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Pendapat Pelapor\\n                    </div>\\n                    <button\\n                      type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                      onClick={() => {\\n                        const current = watchEdit('suggestion') || [];\\n                        setValueEdit('suggestion', [\\n                          ...current,\\n                          { suggestion: '' },\\n                        ]);\\n                      }}\\n                      style={{\\n                        background: 'none',\\n                        border: 'none',\\n                        color: 'var(--primary)',\\n                        fontWeight: '600',\\n                        cursor: 'pointer',\\n                        padding: 0,\\n                        fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      + Tambah Pendapat\\n                    </button>\\n                  </div>\\n                  {(watchEdit('suggestion') || []).length > 0 ? (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        display: 'flex',\\n                        flexDirection: 'column',\\n                        gap: '0.75rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      {(watchEdit('suggestion') || []).map((item, index) => (\\n                        <div\\n                          key={index}\\n                          style={{\\n                            width: '100%',\\n                            paddingLeft: 16,\\n                            paddingRight: 16,\\n                            paddingTop: 11,\\n                            paddingBottom: 11,\\n                            background: 'white',\\n                            overflow: 'hidden',\\n                            borderRadius: 10,\\n                            outline: '1px #E6E9F0 solid',\\n                            outlineOffset: '-1px',\\n                            justifyContent: 'space-between',\\n                            alignItems: 'center',\\n                            gap: 8,\\n                            display: 'flex',\\n                          }}\\n                        >\\n                          <input\\n                            type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                            placeholder=\\\"Masukkan catatan\\\"\\n                            value={item.suggestion || ''}\\n                            onChange={(e) => {\\n                              const current = watchEdit('suggestion') || [];\\n                              const updated = current.map((item, i) =>\\n                                i === index\\n                                  ? { ...item, suggestion: e.target.value }\\n                                  : item,\\n                              );\\n                              setValueEdit('suggestion', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              flex: '1 1 0',\\n                              color: item.suggestion ? '#050505' : '#A0A3AA',\\n                              fontSize: 14,\\n                              fontFamily: 'Inter',\\n                              fontWeight: '400',\\n                              lineHeight: '19.60px',\\n                              wordWrap: 'break-word',\\n                              border: 'none',\\n                              outline: 'none',\\n                              background: 'transparent',\\n                            }}\\n                          />\\n                          <button\\n                            type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                            onClick={() => {\\n                              const updated = (\\n                                watchEdit('suggestion') || []\\n                              ).filter((_, i) => i !== index);\\n                              setValueEdit('suggestion', updated);\\n                            }}\\n                            style={{\\n                              width: 16,\\n                              height: 16,\\n                              position: 'relative',\\n                              background: 'none',\\n                              border: 'none',\\n                              cursor: 'pointer',\\n                              padding: 0,\\n                              display: 'flex',\\n                              alignItems: 'center',\\n                              justifyContent: 'center',\\n                            }}\\n                          >\\n                            <i className=\\\"ph ph-x\\\" style={{ fontSize: 16 }} />\\n                          </button>\\n                        </div>\\n                      ))}\\n                    </div>\\n                  ) : (\\n                    <div\\n                      style={{\\n                        padding: '1rem',\\n                        textAlign: 'center',\\n                        color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                        backgroundColor: 'var(--black-25)',\\n                        borderRadius: '0.5rem',\\n                        border: '1px dashed var(--black-100)',\\n                        fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                      }}\\n                    >\\n                      Belum ada Pendapat Pelapor. Klik \\\"Tambah Pendapat\\\" untuk\\n                      menambahkan.\\n                    </div>\\n                  )}\\n                </Form.Group>\\n                {/* Pemeriksa */}\\n                <div className=\\\"d-flex flex-column gap-3 w-100\\\">\\n                  <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-4\\\">Pelapor</TitleInput>\\n                  {/* Nama dan Pangkat */}\\n                  <Row className=\\\"g-3 w-100\\\">\\n                    <Form.Group>\\n                      <TitleInput className=\\\"mb-3\\\">Sandi</TitleInput>\\n                      <StyledInput\\n                        type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                        placeholder=\\\"Sandi\\\"\\n                        {...registerEdit('password')}\\n                      />\\n                    </Form.Group>\\n                  </Row>\\n                </div>\\n              </>\\n            )}\\n\\n            {/* STEP 3 - Infosus: Paraf */}\\n            {step === 3 && selectedTipeLaporan === 'Infosus' && (\\n              <Form.Group className=\\\"w-100\\\">\\n                <div\\n                  className=\\\"d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center\\\"\\n                  style={{ marginBottom: '1.43rem' }}\\n                >\\n                  <div\\n                    style={{\\n                      color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                      fontSize: '1.14286rem',\\n                      fontWeight: '600',\\n                      textAlign: 'center',\\n                    }}\\n                  >\\n                    Paraf\\n                  </div>\\n                  <button\\n                    type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                    onClick={() => {\\n                      const current = watchEdit('sign') || [];\\n                      setValueEdit('sign', [...current, { sign: '' }]);\\n                    }}\\n                    style={{\\n                      background: 'none',\\n                      border: 'none',\\n                      color: 'var(--primary)',\\n                      fontWeight: '600',\\n                      cursor: 'pointer',\\n                      padding: 0,\\n                      fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                    }}\\n                  >\\n                    + Tambah Paraf\\n                  </button>\\n                </div>\\n                {(watchEdit('sign') || []).length > 0 ? (\\n                  <div\\n                    style={{\\n                      display: 'flex',\\n                      flexDirection: 'column',\\n                      gap: '0.75rem',\\n                    }}\\n                  >\\n                    {(watchEdit('sign') || []).map((item, index) => (\\n                      <div\\n                        key={index}\\n                        style={{\\n                          width: '100%',\\n                          paddingLeft: 16,\\n                          paddingRight: 16,\\n                          paddingTop: 11,\\n                          paddingBottom: 11,\\n                          background: 'white',\\n                          overflow: 'hidden',\\n                          borderRadius: 10,\\n                          outline: '1px #E6E9F0 solid',\\n                          outlineOffset: '-1px',\\n                          justifyContent: 'space-between',\\n                          alignItems: 'center',\\n                          gap: 8,\\n                          display: 'flex',\\n                        }}\\n                      >\\n                        <input\\n                          type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                          placeholder=\\\"Masukkan Paraf\\\"\\n                          value={item.sign || ''}\\n                          onChange={(e) => {\\n                            const current = watchEdit('sign') || [];\\n                            const updated = current.map((item, i) =>\\n                              i === index\\n                                ? { ...item, sign: e.target.value }\\n                                : item,\\n                            );\\n                            setValueEdit('sign', updated);\\n                          }}\\n                          style={{\\n                            flex: '1 1 0',\\n                            color: item.sign ? '#050505' : '#A0A3AA',\\n                            fontSize: 14,\\n                            fontFamily: 'Inter',\\n                            fontWeight: '400',\\n                            lineHeight: '19.60px',\\n                            wordWrap: 'break-word',\\n                            border: 'none',\\n                            outline: 'none',\\n                            background: 'transparent',\\n                          }}\\n                        />\\n                        <button\\n                          type=\\\"button\\\"\\n                          onClick={() => {\\n                            const updated = (watchEdit('sign') || []).filter(\\n                              (_, i) => i !== index,\\n                            );\\n                            setValueEdit('sign', updated);\\n                          }}\\n                          style={{\\n                            width: 16,\\n                            height: 16,\\n                            position: 'relative',\\n                            background: 'none',\\n                            border: 'none',\\n                            cursor: 'pointer',\\n                            padding: 0,\\n                            display: 'flex',\\n                            alignItems: 'center',\\n                            justifyContent: 'center',\\n                          }}\\n                        >\\n                          <i className=\\\"ph ph-x\\\" style={{ fontSize: 16 }} />\\n                        </button>\\n                      </div>\\n                    ))}\\n                  </div>\\n                ) : (\\n                  <div\\n                    style={{\\n                      padding: '1rem',\\n                      textAlign: 'center',\\n                      color: 'var(--black-400)',\\n                      backgroundColor: 'var(--black-25)',\\n                      borderRadius: '0.5rem',\\n                      border: '1px dashed var(--black-100)',\\n                      fontSize: '0.875rem',\\n                    }}\\n                  >\\n                    Belum ada Paraf. Klik \\\"Tambah Paraf\\\" untuk menambahkan.\\n                  </div>\\n                )}\\n              </Form.Group>\\n            )}\\n          </ModalBody>\\n          <ModalFooter>\\n            <ProgressWrapper>\\n              <ProgressBase>\\n                <ProgressFill step={step} maxStep={maxStep} />\\n              </ProgressBase>\\n            </ProgressWrapper>\\n            <div className=\\\"d-flex gap-3\\\">\\n              {step === 1 && (\\n                <Button\\n                  variant=\\\"outline-primary\\\"\\n                  onClick={handleCloseWithReset}\\n                >\\n                  Batal\\n                </Button>\\n              )}\\n              {step > 1 && (\\n                <Button variant=\\\"outline-secondary\\\" onClick={handlePrevious}>\\n                  Kembali\\n                </Button>\\n              )}\\n              {step < maxStep ? (\\n                <Button variant=\\\"primary\\\" onClick={handleNext}>\\n                  Selanjutnya\\n                </Button>\\n              ) : (\\n                <Button\\n                  variant=\\\"primary\\\"\\n                  onClick={handleSubmitEdit(onSubmitEdit)}\\n                  disabled={loading}\\n                >\\n                  {loading ? 'Menyimpan...' : 'Simpan'}\\n                </Button>\\n              )}\\n            </div>\\n          </ModalFooter>\\n        </Form>\\n      </StyledModal>\\n    </>\\n  );\\n}\\n\\nconst Divinder = styled.div`\\n  width: 100%;\\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n  margin-top:1.42857rem;\\n  margin-bottom:1.42857rem;\\n\\n`;\\n\\nconst FormStyle = styled(Form.Group)`\\n    margin-bottom: 1.14rem;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoDisplayContainer = styled.div`\\n  width: 100%;\\n  flex:1;\\n  padding: 16px;\\n  background: var(--white);\\n  // border-bottom: 1px solid var(--Border-Primary, #E6E9F0);\\n  display: flex;\\n  flex-direction: column;\\n  gap: 8px;\\n    max-height:41rem;\\n  overflow-y:auto;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoRow = styled.div`\\n  display: flex;\\n  gap: 4px;\\n  align-items: flex-start;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoLabel = styled.div`\\n  width: 320px;\\n  color: var(--black-500, #64748b);\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  font-weight: 400;\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n  flex-shrink: 0;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoValue = styled.div`\\n  flex: 1;\\n  color: var(--black-900, #0f172a);\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  font-weight: 400;\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n  word-wrap: break-word;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoDivider = styled.div`\\n  width: 100%;\\n  height: 0;\\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoSection = styled.div`\\n  display: flex;\\n  flex-direction: column;\\n  gap: 8px;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoSectionTitle = styled.div`\\n  color: var(--black-900, #0f172a);\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  font-style: normal;\\n  font-weight: 600;\\n  line-height: 1.4rem;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoText = styled.div`\\n  color: var(--black-900, #0f172a);\\n  word-wrap: break-word;\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  font-style: normal;\\n  font-weight: 400;\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n`;\\n\\nconst InfoListItem = styled.div`\\n  display: flex;\\n  gap: 4px;\\n  width: 100%;\\n\\n  &:not(:last-child) {\\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\\n  }\\n`;\\n\\n// Modal Style\\nconst ProgressWrapper = styled.div`\\n  flex: 1;\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n`;\\n\\nconst ProgressBase = styled.div`\\n  width: 5.71429rem;\\n  height: 0.57143rem;\\n  background-color: var(--primary-50);\\n  border-radius: 1.71429rem;\\n  position: relative;\\n  overflow: hidden;\\n`;\\n\\nconst ErrorText = styled.span`\\n  color: var(--danger);\\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\\n  margin-top: 0.25rem;\\n  display: block;\\n`;\\n\\nconst ProgressFill = styled.div`\\n  position: absolute;\\n  top: 0;\\n  left: 0;\\n  height: 100%;\\n  width: ${(props) => {\\n    switch (props.step) {\\n      case 1:\\n        return '33%';\\n      case 2:\\n        return '66%';\\n      case 3:\\n        return '100%';\\n      default:\\n        return '0%';\\n    }\\n  }};\\n  background-color: var(--primary-500);\\n  transition: width 0.4s ease;\\n  border-radius: 1.71429rem;\\n`;\\n\\nconst StyledModal = styled(Modal)`\\n  .modal-dialog {\\n    max-width: 670px;\\n  }\\n\\n  .modal-content {\\n    display: flex;\\n    flex-direction: column;\\n  }\\n`;\\nconst ModalHeader = styled(Modal.Header)`\\n  display: flex;\\n  padding: 0.8rem 1.33333rem;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 1.06667rem;\\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n  flex-shrink: 0;\\n`;\\n\\nconst ModalBody = styled(Modal.Body)`\\n  display: flex;\\n  padding: 1.06667rem 1.33333rem;\\n  flex-direction: column;\\n  align-items: flex-start;\\n  gap: 1.33333rem;\\n\\n  max-height: 45rem;\\n  overflow-y: auto;\\n  flex: 1;\\n  min-height: 0;\\n`;\\n\\nconst ModalFooter = styled(Modal.Footer)`\\n  display: flex;\\n  padding: 0.8rem 1.33333rem 1.06667rem 1.33333rem;\\n  justify-content: flex-end;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.53333rem;\\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n  flex-shrink: 0;\\n`;\\n\\nconst TitleHeader = styled.p`\\n  color: var(--black);\\n  font-size: 1.14286remrem;\\n\\n  font-style: normal;\\n  font-weight: 600;\\n  line-height: 150%;\\n  margin: 0;\\n`;\\n\\nconst DescHeader = styled.p`\\n  color: var(--black-400);\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  font-style: normal;\\n  font-weight: 400;\\n  line-height: 150%;\\n  margin: 0;\\n`;\\n\\nconst WrappIcon = styled.div`\\n  display: flex;\\n  padding: 0.53333rem;\\n  justify-content: center;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  gap: 0.66667rem;\\n  border-radius: 0.53333rem;\\n  border: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n`;\\n\\nconst RadioButtonContainer = styled.div`\\n  border: 1px solid ${({ isSelected }) => (isSelected ? 'var(--primary)' : 'var(--black-100)')};\\n  border-radius: 0.57143rem;\\n  padding: 0.4rem 0.53333rem;\\n  gap: 0.1rem;\\n  position: relative;\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n  cursor: pointer;\\n\\n  .form-check-input {\\n    position: relative;\\n    margin-left: 0;\\n    margin-top: 0;\\n  }\\n\\n  p {\\n    font-size: 0.85714rem;\\n    font-style: normal;\\n    font-weight: 600;\\n    margin: 0;\\n    color: ${({ isSelected }) => (isSelected ? 'var(--primary)' : 'var(--black)')};\\n  }\\n`;\\n\\nconst FormCheckStyled = styled(Form.Check)`\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n\\n  .form-check-input {\\n    margin-right: 0.5rem;\\n\\n    &:checked {\\n      background-color: var(--primary);\\n      border-color: var(--primary);\\n    }\\n  }\\n`;\\nconst TitleInput = styled.div`\\ncolor: var(--black);\\nfont-size: 1rem;\\nfont-weight: 500;\\nline-height: 140%;\\n\\n`;\\n\\nconst StyledInput = styled(Form.Control)`\\n  width: 100%;\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\\n  border-radius: 0.5rem;\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n  border: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n  box-shadow: none;\\n\\n  &:focus {\\n    border-color: var(--primary-500);\\n  }\\n`;\\n\\nconst StyledTextarea = styled.textarea`\\n  width: 100%;\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\\n  border-radius: 0.5rem;\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n  border: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n  font-family:Inter;\\n  box-shadow: none;\\n\\n  &:focus {\\n    border-color: var(--primary-500);\\n  }\\n`;\\nconst CustomStyledTextarea = styled.textarea`\\n  width: 100%;\\n  font-size: 1rem;\\n  border-radius: 0.5rem;\\n  line-height: 1.5;\\n  font-family: Inter;\\n\\n  border: none;\\n  outline: none;\\n  box-shadow: none;\\n  background: transparent;\\n\\n  resize: none;\\n\\n  &:focus {\\n    outline: none;\\n    box-shadow: none;\\n  }\\n`;\\n\\nconst LabelInput = styled.label`\\n  color: var(--black);\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  font-weight: 500;\\n  line-height: 140%;\\n  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\\n  display: block;\\n`;\\n\\nconst SignatureBox = styled.div`\\n  background: var(--black-25);\\n  border: 1px solid var(--black-100);\\n  border-radius: 0.75rem;\\n  padding: 0.75rem;\\n  gap:0.5rem;\\n  // margin-top: 8px;\\n`;\\n\\nconst SignatureText = styled.span`\\n  font-weight: 400;\\n  gap:0.5rem;\\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\\n  color: var(--black);\\n  display: block;\\n  // min-height: 40px;\\n  display: flex;\\n  align-items: center;\\n`;\\n\",\"html\":\"\"},\"sourceInfo\":\"\",\"sourceInfoUrl\":\"\",\"hideSource\":false,\"data\":{\"title\":\"\",\"sourceType\":\"\"},\"fullscreen\":false,\"hideWidget\":true,\"dateFields\":\"\",\"useAsFilterConfig\":{\"enable\":false}},\"x\":0,\"y\":348},{\"chartConfig\":{},\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-16 10:46:02.323000\",\"createdBy\":\"074fd5f6f6ad928bec90e9ce68f19073\",\"dashboardId\":\"1769155096865\",\"description\":\"\",\"fieldMapping\":null,\"filtersConfig\":null,\"group\":null,\"h\":5,\"id\":\"145241a806c51ae5fe1f2283e06105aa\",\"menuId\":\"01f63e60376afe827638ed614e1cea76\",\"metaData\":{\"params\":{\"connectionId\":\"\",\"queryId\":\"\",\"chart\":\"react-js\"}},\"name\":\"Widget Aksi\",\"parentId\":null,\"referenceId\":null,\"referenceType\":null,\"responsive\":{\"1024\":{\"x\":11,\"y\":0,\"w\":1,\"h\":5}},\"styleType\":null,\"tags\":null,\"thumbnail\":null,\"type\":\"react-js\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-07-13 15:58:26.006000\",\"updatedBy\":\"3c04f304c5e949d5cc0d54bfb06a6f8d\",\"w\":1,\"widgetConfig\":{\"collectionGroup\":\"react-js\",\"styleType\":\"react-js\",\"visualizationType\":\"react-js\",\"showTitle\":false,\"handler\":false,\"hideMobile\":true,\"mapInsight\":false,\"cacheEnabled\":false,\"enableCache\":false,\"developer\":{\"enabledReact\":true,\"enabled\":false,\"css\":\"\",\"js\":\"\",\"react\":\"import { Dropdown, ButtonGroup, Modal } from 'react-bootstrap';\\nimport styled from 'styled-components';\\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';\\nimport { useNotification } from 'notification.hooks';\\nimport { usePermission } from '@app/hooks/permission.hook';\\n\\n// IMPORT DYNAMIC FORM\\nimport TerimaLaporan from 'widget:efbfa3239be4efc03f0f2b70fadc983c';\\nimport TolakLaporan from 'widget:3ef300c032e24733ba0e247e4095c199';\\nimport KirimHasilGelarMabes from 'widget:f63827766c7202e1119ac1f2e71c595f';\\nimport TambahLaporForm from 'widget:7e8fb6a3cf5a93e6ced34c36384fef4e';\\nimport KirimSubbidProvos from 'widget:f6a5439d7094c008762669641fd70b8f';\\nimport LimpahPerkara from 'widget:18cd078b10e4daabf73182fdbd3d45ba';\\n\\nimport Limpah from 'widget:e3d8da241f2a1515a4035332f368db27';\\nimport LimpahPolda from 'widget:06af554e129ccaf1df72cbebd0955917';\\nimport VerifikasiUnit from 'widget:988aff80d5ea6efc6b723f624a9de240';\\nimport Revisi from 'widget:cb4b2ce720eec748f0f7fe8e8086dae0';\\nimport VerifikasiSubUnit from 'widget:791aac092f9bf80c5deb14b7516f08e6';\\nimport VerifikasiUnitPolda from 'widget:0baf07077d3fdadd596c075944ffbed3';\\nimport Tolak from 'widget:56fd696f762728905a289b1150dfab3d';\\nimport LimpahBiroWassidik from 'widget:365b5465523cc4275fb6e18120b6f64f';\\n\\nimport ModalLanjutLidik from 'widget:7e8b4b69780c8d60552bca23b17ec5dc';\\nimport ModalLidik from 'widget:51844be888ce422547ccd397b2351086';\\nimport ModalGelarLidik from 'widget:891fb9bfec4c4c78f5cd80fa755e42b6';\\nimport KirimHasilGelarPolda from 'widget:3d485f6d7ece734649ba8f182249267b';\\nimport KirimHasilGelarPolres from 'widget:643ed9f36d8fbbc9c4095a19b97469d8';\\nimport LanjutkanLaporan from 'widget:e57f602be5a8deb089f4f41ea560c06a';\\nimport ModalGelarPerkara from 'widget:2beaf2e5b4fed2f92bde20632195079e';\\nimport ModalGelarPerkaraRj from 'widget:e19b52f6e4b7369ddcc28aa6a486f1f4';\\nimport ModalHasilGelarRj from 'widget:35a1d5e5d3ac9011c1c1d73d70e6df4e';\\n\\nimport RiksaCepat from 'widget:c39475a9200c87fe04d8dd70b88a3cbf';\\nimport PemberkasanForm from 'widget:1f9b40c758e450c7b3edc2cba308ac27';\\nimport ProsesSidangDisiplinForm from 'widget:0aa2a12fca00a3790adbc018dc14092a';\\nimport HasilSidangDisiplinForm from 'widget:87388490785a5cc8ac8f4be6e02af80f';\\nimport ProsesSidangKKEPForm from 'widget:b97de6b79e5f1eae731a16e79658dd7c';\\nimport HasilSidangKKEPForm from 'widget:549b38e20f8189b4c21644eea902f5a3';\\nimport BandingForm from 'widget:06460af90be14a5fef1da93004c123ad';\\nimport TolakBandingForm from 'widget:9c5e58f4417bfafa37d966dc248117bf';\\nimport KeberataForm from 'widget:fcf25e3f5d15495373ef8f69980ee452';\\nimport TidakKeberatanForm from 'widget:097647dd24126972f1d95aad89715ce2';\\nimport LimpahBagRehabpersForm from 'widget:de7b4b6eb46d30ff85b5b346236383f6';\\n\\nimport TerimaDanTeruskan from 'widget:ca69cd4914cb86af996a9972c71bdfe6';\\nimport RevisiLimpah from 'widget:99ae71520404b2e7e682c96b2a229094';\\nimport Pencabutan from 'widget:7bb7895e259a92d53349c835059a0a45';\\nimport PencabutanSebelumSprinLidik from 'widget:aa76893a4ec97c184e8f51a40bdea7d6';\\nimport PencabutanSetelahSprinLidik from 'widget:4b1ca7a5552688cb23bd89d880db3747';\\nimport GelarPencabutan from 'widget:668c9f9956b0e2f186b6b3924042182a';\\nimport RestorativeJustice from 'widget:c59321e1c5f590a6e9cfa7eef2ec9eb2';\\nimport LimpahBiroProvos from 'widget:73d1215ac3bdf487d2c8687bdc0fe363';\\nimport LimpahSubbidProvos from 'widget:41ae8a10da61c5a5deb6728908ed74f4';\\nimport ModalEditLaporan from 'widget:b2c7e40a099beac96302fb9a69d0c9c4';\\nimport LimpahKabid from 'widget:cacb81bc4807db41d72019fa7eaaf671';\\nimport LimpahBiro from 'widget:77544b9a7045ed53102b430b0b537d06';\\nimport VerifikasiSurat from 'widget:9f1a26c371cc9533d9d4a8dbde4e1295';\\nimport LimpahPolres from 'widget:441fd779e9230b30b0378f4576f12a0f';\\nimport KembaliKabid from 'widget:4b7c930cfe00f621a97f4a68da78fbe8';\\nimport LimpahYanduan from 'widget:87a3d2190b